org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.graph.bpel
Class AeBpelActivityCoordinates

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.graph.bpel.AeBpelActivityCoordinates
public class AeBpelActivityCoordinates
extends java.lang.Object

A simple object that contains a BPEL activity's bounding rectangle, the activity model and its location path. This is used for hit testing. The coordinates of the bounding rectangle is relative to the root container.
